data.description: Who's been looking for a move in ready home in the Greenwood School district? This one located in the Williamson Place addition is looking for a new owner! This three bed two bath has a split floor plan. The master bedroom has all you need with a large bathroom and huge walk in closet. So many renovations have been completed in the last year including a kitchen renovation in 2020 and a new roof and water heater 2023. In the backyard you will find a covered porch and a storm shelter. Reach out for a full list on renovation items.
